Dear all,

we are looking for a postdoc. The joint file describe the subject which
concerns the prevention of suicide by mining social networks.
Complete applications with attachments should be sent by email
<mailto:drh-euro-recrut@umontpellier.fr> *before the 18th of January
2016 *at drh-euro-recrut@umontpellier.fr.
Detailled information are available here:
http://www.umontpellier.fr/portfolio/appel-a-projets-post-doc/

Applicants should also contact supervisors:
Jérôme Azé <jerome.aze@lirmm.fr>
and Sandra Bringay <sandra.bringay@lirmm.fr>

Eligible applicants should hold a PhD or equivalent doctoral level
degree from a university outside the Montpellier school district.
The selected candidate should be able to start their position from March
2016.
The fellowship is for one year (with the possibility to be renewed once
for another 12 months).

Best regards
Jérôme Azé and Sandra Bringay

